<SYNC Start=3069><P Class=ENCC>
It's so weird. How did Joey<br>
end up kissing Charlie last night?
<SYNC Start=6835><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=7007><P Class=ENCC>
- I thought you'd end up kissing Charlie.<br>
