to belong to the late Shania Twain.
<SYNC Start=222254><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=225258><P Class=ENCC>
Phoebe, Shania Twain is still alive.
<SYNC Start=227692><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=228628><P Class=ENCC>
Oh, then I overpaid.
<SYNC Start=230459><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=233233><P Class=ENCC>
