- I promise.
<SYNC Start=314045><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=314247><P Class=ENCC>
- Thank you.<br>
- Well, I am going hunting.
<SYNC Start=317808><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
